Tyrant- (5)
- Starts the game off as a powerless person, but then slowly gains more power as they die.
- Upon dying once, they gain the ability to learn the role of a person every other night. (Cooldown 2 phases)
- Upon dying twice, they lose the ability to invest roles, but gain the ability to weak protect a person each night.
- Upon dying a third time, they unlock the ability to weak protect or weak attack a person in the night. Dying furthur does not unlock any new powers.
- Investing is instant, Protecting and attacking are both night end and visiting actions.
- Respawns in 2 phases when the outlaw has no powers, 4 phases until they have some powers, and 6 phases after they have died 3 times.
